data.description: Back on Market!! Financing fell through. Come home to this fantastic updated 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath home nestled on an over half an acre with Private Screened in Pool, a picturesque Lutz community featuring unique homes on larger lots, lush park like landscaping, No Deed Restrictions and No HOA fees!!  First Floor Bedroom with Full Bath, 3 Bedrooms on 2nd Fl including Oversized Double Master bedroom with Exercise Room!  Fantastic covered lanai and pool area have plenty of room to enjoy outdoor living and are perfect for entertaining!  Lots of storage room in the oversized 3-car garage! with Stairs leading to 2nd Floor Storage Room / Bonus Room.    This house is lacking new owners to bring this gem back to life!! Bring your best ideas to life with this home and reap the rewards of customization and personal touch including everything Lutz has to offer.Enjoy relaxed country living, yet just minutes to interstates, USF, Moffitt, VA & Florida Hospitals, restaurants, abundant shopping, and Tampa Premium Outlets! Convenient to shopping and highways.
